item.name: 1_Authenticate

request.description: Perform authentication and populate the variable specified in the {{bigip_token_var}} variable.

item.description:
Authenticate to a BIG-IP device.

Input Variables:
bigip_mgmt      BIG-IP management address
bigip_username    Username
bigip_password    Password
bigip_token_timeout  [OPTIONAL] Timeout for the auth token

Output Variables:
bigip_token      Authentication token

request.description: Not strictly necessary but useful to see the status of the package in the GUI.

item.name: Download the AS3 Package to BIG-IP

request.description: Request installs the RPM on the BIG-IP. This will not be necessary once AS3 container support is added in subsequent versions.
See if the RPM install procedure finished successfully.

exec: tests["AS3 selfTest Passed"] = respData[0].message =  "all tests passed";

request.description:
Run the built-in AS3 selfTest.

Note the following from the Docs:
"If an error displays, this is an indication that AS3 is not entirely compatible with your BIG-IP software version or module provisioning. This does not necessarily imply that you cannot use AS3 successfully."
